------------------------------------------

botbits explore the digital dimension between humans, robots and software.
they are created by hansjakobwagner and supplied for free in both original 16x16 px editions and artificially blown up 1600x1600 px single editions on the following day. 
remaining botbits will be eaten by a real robot after all editions are minted.

------------------------------------------

thanks to all the industrious bots and/or humans - it was a great pleasure to provide some fun tiny bits for free. with botbit1 we are now coming to the closing of the prelude to the botbit project. stay tuned for more. I am stoked to see what will happen next!
